page.title: 19CLUBS AND SOCIETIES
page.content: This is a list of all the clubs, associations and societies active in Bentham in 1985:-{Clubs}cricket, squash, tennis, bowls, football, netball, snooker, golf, darts, badminton(Low Bentham and Wenning Clubs), pigeon, youth, sports, Labour, Liberal and Conservative.{Societies} old age pensioners, W.I., Agricultural, Low B. Horticultural, Abbeyfield, Young Farmers, Photographic, playing field, playgroup, Ewecross Historical, NSPCC and the Agricultural Discussion Soc. { {Unclassified}Pantomime group, Victoria Institute, Playing Field Ass., Meals on Wheels, Playscheme, Collingwood and Longstaffe Charity, ARC, Angling Ass., Aid to Sickness Fund, Girl Guides, Cubs and Brownies.
